Launch an interactive msfconsole to ientify an exploit for the application (Do not use searchsploit). achieved_list: Use NMAP to identify the target machine (192.168.5.2) among (192.168.5.0/24)

Find the exploit using Metasploit: spring_framework_rce_spring4shell
Configure the exploit target host RHOSTS 192.168.5.2
Find the flag: read the flag
remaining_list: Interact with the web server discovering the service: Spring 5.3.17 or Tomcat 8.5.77
